<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<h3>About this demo</h3>

<ul>
    <li><b>Devices</b> page shows registered LattePanda IOTA devices.</li>
    <li><b>Publish Config</b> publishes a new desired config version (device or group).</li>
    <li>The device agent polls for config changes, applies them, and reports <code>AppliedConfigVersion</code>.</li>
</ul>

<p class="text-muted">
    Tip: Publish a config update (e.g., samplingMs=500) and watch the device state update within seconds.
</p>